      </section>
      <section>
        <num>27.24.060</num>
        <heading>YARD AREAS.</heading>
        <text>Unless otherwise provided in this chapter, the regulations in the R3 district shall apply. (Ord. 1985-3 § 3, 1985; prior code § 146.05(F)).</text>
      </section>
      <section>
        <num>27.24.070</num>
        <heading>DWELLING STANDARDS.</heading>
