      <container>
        <prefix>ARTICLE</prefix>
        <num>II</num>
        <heading>R-5D DISTRICT—MULTIPLE-FAMILY DWELLINGS FOR DOWNTOWN (HIGH DENSITY)</heading>
        <section>
          <num>27.28.040</num>
          <heading>PERMITTED USES.</heading>
          <text>Use of buildings, or land shall be limited to the uses permitted in R1, R2, R3, R4, R4-D, or R5 Districts. (Ord. 1986-14 § 1, 1986).</text>
        </section>
        <section>
          <num>27.28.042</num>
          <heading>SPECIAL USES.</heading>
          <para>
            <num>(1)</num>
            <text>Special uses allowed in R1, R2, R3, R4, R4-D, or R5 Districts. (Ord. 1986-14 § 1, 1986).</text>
          </para>
        </section>
        <section>
          <num>27.28.044</num>
          <heading>OFF-STREET PARKING.</heading>
          <text>Off-street parking facilities shall be provided as required in Chapter 27.64 subject to the design standards in Chapter 27.25 in the R4-D district. (Ord. 1986-14 § 1, 1986).</text>
        </section>
        <section>
          <num>27.28.046</num>
          <heading>MINIMUM DEVELOPMENT STANDARDS.</heading>
